  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "一 “文化大革命”引发的历史反思",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26321245_7_2584-2612",
          "range": "2584-2612",
          "rangeStart": 2584,
          "rangeEnd": 2612,
          "markText": "物质利益原则仍然是调动积极性以加快发展的最直接有效的手段",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691452592,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-08 07:56:32",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2612",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2612"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_11_4540-4617",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4540-4617",
      "markText": "王震高兴地说：“我看英国搞得不错，物质极大丰富，三大差别基本消灭，社会公正、社会福利也受重视，如果再加上共产党执政，英国就是我们理想中的共产主义社会了。”",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4540&rangeEnd=4617",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4540&rangeEnd=4617"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_6_680-762",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "680-762",
      "markText": "当然，如果没有“文革”，启动改革不可能获得这么大的推力。而如果没有大批人员出国考察感受到的挑战和机遇，中国领导人也不会有那么强烈的紧迫感，要达成改革共识会困难得多。",
      "totalCount": 403,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=680&rangeEnd=762",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=680&rangeEnd=762"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_8_1334-1385",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1334-1385",
      "markText": "尽管不少人对统计数据存有疑问，我仍愿相信“文革”后公布的数据大体准确，“崩溃边缘”的说法太过政治化了。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1334&rangeEnd=1385",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1334&rangeEnd=1385"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_31_2270-2307",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "2270-2307",
      "markText": "改革的推动力是巨大的，但是改革不是点金术，经济关系的变动不能代替物质投入。",
      "totalCount": 368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2270&rangeEnd=2307",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2270&rangeEnd=2307"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_7_1410-1478",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1410-1478",
      "markText": "“文革”带来了两大灾难性后果：一是伤人太多，它把所有的阶层，特别是精英阶层伤害了；二是老百姓生活太苦了，民生问题已经成为重大的政治问题。",
      "totalCount": 363,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1410&rangeEnd=1478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1410&rangeEnd=1478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_17_1846-1897",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "1846-1897",
      "markText": "政府发觉，企业有了自己的独立利益后，总是倾向于企业自身的眼前利益，而忽视企业的长期发展和对国家的责任。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1846&rangeEnd=1897",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=1846&rangeEnd=1897"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_7_2584-2612",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2584-2612",
      "markText": "物质利益原则仍然是调动积极性以加快发展的最直接有效的手段",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_14_652-679",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "652-679",
      "markText": "这种长期的对农业的净提取，是中国农村长期贫困的原因之一",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=652&rangeEnd=679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=652&rangeEnd=679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_34_413-502",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "413-502",
      "markText": "中国的改革不是依据理论预设，而是诉诸实践和试验，从局部开始，渐进式推进。但这并不意味可以忽视观念和理论突破的意义，理论观念一旦取得突破，必会形成新的思想力量，为改革打开更大空间。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26321245&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=413&rangeEnd=502",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/238328807191a15d238d15b?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=413&rangeEnd=502"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26321245_21_1566-1625",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "1566-1625",
